        {
            "title": "海皇粥店結業︱創辦人再發帖 : 將發出無力償還聲明  冀員工體諒共度難關",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"海皇粥店結業︱創辦人再發帖 : 將發出無力償還聲明  冀盡量加快發放欠薪流程。資料圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/d4567ace6472a9ef39ef772bf213ba5a/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250510/_2025051019213288588.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">海皇粥店結業︱創辦人再發帖 : 將發出無力償還聲明  冀盡量加快發放欠薪流程。資料圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>【海皇粥店/創辦人/勞工處/破欠】海皇粥店日前突然全線結業，近百名員工慘遭拖糧，涉及金額約1,500萬元。海皇粥店創辦人蕭楚基和蔡汪浩今日（10日）再於社交平台發文，稱明白員工關注薪酬及遣散費等問題，向全體員工致以最深歉意，並承諾將全力配合勞工處及相關機構，保障員工法定權益。有網民留言斥二人不負責任，要政府「埋單」賠償員工。\n\n</p><h2>將發出無力償還聲明  破欠基金會盡量加快發放欠薪流程</h2>\n<p>兩人表示，已於昨日通過自願性清盤並委託清盤人負責整個流程，至於勞資賠償方面，已與勞工處完成會議，所有員工的薪金、代通知金及遣散費等數目，將會加快完成核算，同時將發出無力償還聲明，破產欠薪保障基金在收到相關聲明後，將會安排與各員工核對數目，並盡量加快發放欠薪流程。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4241105/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"皇粥店創辦人蕭楚基和蔡汪浩今日（10日）再於社交平台發文。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5255b7592afcd7a86fda3c47762ee0e1/2025-05/12345.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        皇粥店創辦人蕭楚基和蔡汪浩今日（10日）再於社交平台發文。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4241109/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"海皇粥店創辦人蕭楚基(右)和蔡汪浩。資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/96b3d70d252149cd0a93a42f4bcb9385/2025-05/452045204125_0.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海皇粥店創辦人蕭楚基(右)和蔡汪浩。資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"sthl-ur\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4239990/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"海皇粥店日前突然結業。資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8b1980cea791a2dc7bd9d8c6e7a1e2f0/2025-05/NS250508OE10.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海皇粥店日前突然結業。資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"sthl-ur\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4239991/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"海皇粥店日前突然結業。資料圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9156910ac2e626e61a90f0208e6368f0/2025-05/KakaoTalk_20250508_163649504_06_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海皇粥店日前突然結業。資料圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4239993/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"海皇粥店創辦人蕭楚基和蔡汪浩昨日已發聲明。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1643516cabdd096fa4e09083deb68975/2025-05/495571414_1105619844707806_6126139941189779170_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海皇粥店創辦人蕭楚基和蔡汪浩昨日已發聲明。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4239992/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"海皇粥店創辦人蕭楚基和蔡汪浩昨發聲明。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6ffdf5b80e704c18753e2ac8db6b2015/2025-05/495566784_1105619831374474_5833558120329756144_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海皇粥店創辦人蕭楚基和蔡汪浩昨發聲明。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4239994/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"海皇粥店創辦人蕭楚基和蔡汪浩昨發聲明。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/06a42c2c76a5db84cccd3439aeef3f4c/2025-05/495574136_1105619814707809_1441890354439015354_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        海皇粥店創辦人蕭楚基和蔡汪浩昨發聲明。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>兩人再次感謝員工多年付出，又說強調艱難決定實屬迫不得已，希望能互相體諒，共度難關。\n\n</p>\n<p>有網民留言批訴二人不負責任，留下爛攤子要政府埋單。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞: <a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/society/3454212/\">海皇粥店結業︱創辦人澄清非無良：已墊支$3000萬填氹 唯一居住物業亦賤賣</a>\n</p>\n<p>               <a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/society/3454320/\">海皇粥店結業︱孫玉菡：破欠基金足以覆蓋員工欠薪金額 若資料齊全3月內可批核</a>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
