        {
            "title": "劉丹爆孫女小糯米密謀驚喜給嫲嫲  避談會否跟楊冪講母親節快樂  譚輝智慶幸參加《中2》否則無得留低",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"劉丹與譚輝智今日（10日）到荃灣出席《愛·回家之開心速遞》活動。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/6ceb5eaa3fae0403c68162f9bbf62dce/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250510/_2025051018303947121.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">劉丹與譚輝智今日（10日）到荃灣出席《愛·回家之開心速遞》活動。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>劉丹、滕麗名、呂慧儀、周嘉洛、古佩玲及樊亦敏等今日（10日）到荃灣出席《愛·回家之開心速遞》活動，吸引過百途人圍觀，眾人除了分享如何慶祝母親節外，亦有玩運球遊戲，以及大派康乃馨給現場觀眾。\n\n</p><h2>預告明天與老婆及劉愷威慶祝</h2>\n<p>活動後，劉丹與譚輝智一起受訪，劉丹表示明天母親節需開工，但幸好早收工，之後可與老婆及兒子劉愷威一起食飯慶祝，又爆孫女小糯米最近在房間神神秘秘，不知道是否預備了驚喜給嫲嫲，至於小糯米是否也會跟媽媽講母親節快樂？丹爺聽後即說：「唔好問呢啲好冇？」\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"一眾演員到荃灣出席《愛·回家之開心速遞》活動，吸引過百途人圍觀。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6cd4779e1422d6fe552fe3e3c6c8be3a/2025-05/IMG-20250510-WA0048.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一眾演員到荃灣出席《愛·回家之開心速遞》活動，吸引過百途人圍觀。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"活動後，劉丹與譚輝智一起受訪，劉丹表示明天母親節需開工。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0f705e3ebe4ee03514ab1274319aa2bb/2025-05/IMG-20250510-WA0052.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        活動後，劉丹與譚輝智一起受訪，劉丹表示明天母親節需開工。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"劉丹又爆孫女小糯米最近在房間神神秘秘，不知道是否預備了驚喜給嫲嫲，\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c4ea380932682a3dac8f5041183ab7be/2025-05/IMG-20250510-WA0057.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉丹又爆孫女小糯米最近在房間神神秘秘，不知道是否預備了驚喜給嫲嫲，\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"至於小糯米是否也會跟媽媽講母親節快樂？丹爺聽後即說：「唔好問呢啲好冇？」\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3323f9c96a601b4e299c1817f51ded06/2025-05/IMG-20250510-WA0060.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        至於小糯米是否也會跟媽媽講母親節快樂？丹爺聽後即說：「唔好問呢啲好冇？」\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"眾人分享如何慶祝母親節。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/563a80686221b7b4ac5bc059298a136c/2025-05/IMG-20250510-WA0074.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        眾人分享如何慶祝母親節。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>幫艾威太太呼籲捐贈肝臟</h2>\n<p>提到同劇的演員秦翊洺早前在食店拍片時因沒事前通知被老闆阻撓，之後更爆衝突，劉丹就表示拍攝先要同人講，這是基本禮貌，又指以前拍攝時借地方很受歡迎、也很熱情，但後來大家的態度轉變了，遇到別人拒絕自己也識做：「行遠啲，唔好夾硬嚟，一定會唔開心收場。」至於艾威太太因情況危急，但仍未找到適合的肝臟，令他在網上呼籲大家捐贈，曾跟艾威合作過的劉丹指不知道，但他指肝可重生，呼籲大家捐贈，也希望對方太太能吉人天相。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"譚輝智就指因開工關係，故上星期已跟媽媽、太太及妹妹等慶祝母親節。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/187e517943a9bba4d703aac215995d80/2025-05/IMG-20250510-WA0043.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        譚輝智就指因開工關係，故上星期已跟媽媽、太太及妹妹等慶祝母親節。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"對於明天將是《中年好聲音3》決賽，問到是否有心水？他指7強也很強。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bedb4b43196652b781c81c3c420a1bca/2025-05/IMG-20250510-WA0045.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        對於明天將是《中年好聲音3》決賽，問到是否有心水？他指7強也很強。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"譚輝智獲不少粉絲到場支持。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6cf9f710b757ecb8dd440470c281d849/2025-05/IMG-20250510-WA0065.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        譚輝智獲不少粉絲到場支持。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"劉丹直言《中3》比《中2》好，又表示看好張與辰、黃博及李金凱。譚輝智就笑謂若參加《中3》，自己便不能坐在這裏。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/97b1c04935218cf14da72bf0dea4142e/2025-05/IMG-20250510-WA0075.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉丹直言《中3》比《中2》好，又表示看好張與辰、黃博及李金凱。譚輝智就笑謂若參加《中3》，自己便不能坐在這裏。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"一眾演員更在台上大玩遊戲。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/928f5fb1167bfb4c85ad5895a548bd33/2025-05/IMG-20250510-WA0083.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一眾演員更在台上大玩遊戲。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"台上玩運球遊戲，以及大派康乃馨給現場觀眾。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6c87804bf70d84b99e67063d04a1145f/2025-05/IMG-20250510-WA0087.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        台上玩運球遊戲，以及大派康乃馨給現場觀眾。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>譚輝智大讚7強犀利</h2>\n<p>譚輝智就指因開工關係，故上星期已跟媽媽、太太及妹妹等慶祝母親節，對於明天將是《中年好聲音3》決賽，問到是否有心水？他指7強也很強，自己也很期待在新場館聽他們唱歌，至於有沒有貼士給他們？輝智笑說：「我邊有？我自己仲驚，佢哋好犀利，啲經驗都好豐富，我當睇騷！」而在旁的劉丹更直言《中3》比《中2》好，又表示看好張與辰、黃博及李金凱。譚輝智就笑謂若參加《中3》，自己便不能坐在這裏。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
