            "title": "維港．雙鑽連沽3伙1房 單日套現逾1719萬",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"維港．雙鑽連沽3伙1房，單日套現逾1719萬。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/f039c30f3013f77de2212304ba0b3f24/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250510/_2025051018384264395.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">維港．雙鑽連沽3伙1房，單日套現逾1719萬。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>中國海外發展的啟德維港．雙鑽今日錄3宗成交，單位單日套現1719.6萬，其中1A座26樓D室，面積305方呎，屬1房(開放式廚房)間隔，以584.2萬元成交，呎價19,154元。\n\n</p>\n<p>而1A座25樓D室，面積305方呎，屬1房(開放式廚房)間隔，以578.5萬元成交，呎價18,967元；最後1A座10樓D室，面積305方呎，屬1房(開放式廚房)間隔，以556.9萬元成交，呎價18,259元。<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2068275/即時-地產-維港-雙鑽連沽3伙1房-單日套現逾1719萬",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-10 18:46:52",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "凱和山錄2宗成交 套現逾1050萬",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"凱和山錄2宗成交，套現逾1050萬。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/ea960dddbcc2b4c1f0fbbb38ab82928b/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250510/_2025051018260126390.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">凱和山錄2宗成交，套現逾1050萬。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>路勁發展的屯門凱和山單日錄2宗成交，涉及3房套及2房戶型，合共套現逾1,050.45萬元，均為同區換樓客；包括5座10樓A室，面積700方呎，屬3房套間隔，成交價為623萬元，呎價8,900元。\n\n</p>\n<p>而3座9樓D室，為2房開放式廚房間隔，面積496方呎，成交價427.45萬元，呎價約8,618元。\n\n</p>\n<p>路勁銷售及市場推廣總監顏景鳳表示，凱和山主打現樓即買即住，配合近期推出的「90天 Chill 級付款辦法」及多元付款選擇，加上市場利好政策及利率有望持續下調，項目對轉租為買及換樓客具有明顯吸引力，帶動銷情穩步上揚。<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2068273/即時-地產-凱和山錄2宗成交-套現逾1050萬",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-10 18:37:33",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "KOKO HILLS辦母親節感謝日",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"KOKO HILLS辦母親節感謝日。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/7f639452d4edffa878dab8f16b69f43a/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250510/_2025051018192918269.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">KOKO HILLS辦母親節感謝日。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>母親節將至，會德豐地產系下項目藍田KOKO HILLS舉辦「KOKO母親節感謝日」，以答謝媽媽們無微不至的關懷和照顧。活動更邀得香港兒童探索博物館策劃「照亮我的媽媽」DIY工作坊，孩子們透過學習鏡子原理，親手製作實用又有趣的禮物送給媽媽；現場一眾媽媽收到後笑逐顏開，十分窩心。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"KOKO HILLS辦母親節感謝日。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f1d150821f99dad3233cd04771df8f65/2025-05/KOKO_HILLS_101_1_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        KOKO HILLS辦母親節感謝日。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"KOKO HILLS辦母親節感謝日。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0c76e0e26883df78a1133e36711083a5/2025-05/KOKO_HILLS_101_2_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        KOKO HILLS辦母親節感謝日。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"KOKO HILLS辦母親節感謝日。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ad882ab84cfe44b453b0c4d60e5d78bb/2025-05/KOKO_HILLS_101_6_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        KOKO HILLS辦母親節感謝日。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"KOKO HILLS辦母親節感謝日。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/17c480d506b0b2565027675a31e444ad/2025-05/KOKO_HILLS_101_7_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        KOKO HILLS辦母親節感謝日。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"KOKO HILLS辦母親節感謝日。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2150297f1e1d2f77efb1311075d4a3fa/2025-05/KOKO_HILLS_101_8_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        KOKO HILLS辦母親節感謝日。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"KOKO HILLS辦母親節感謝日。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/015270eb141e923d89febbb475d00788/2025-05/KOKO_HILLS_101_4_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        KOKO HILLS辦母親節感謝日。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"KOKO HILLS辦母親節感謝日。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2e2c92f4dbdc3ba8b8e43143b8b9899f/2025-05/KOKO_HILLS_101_3_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        KOKO HILLS辦母親節感謝日。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>活動亦為母親們送上「溫暖牌花束」 手工針織花及由社企「糕點時光 Time To Gold」提供養生特飲，讓大人、小朋友都滿載而歸、樂在其中。預祝各位媽媽母親節快樂！\n\n</p><h1>GRAND SEASONS再添成交</h1>\n<p>同系將軍澳日出康城GRAND SEASONS再添成交，為1A座20樓B室，面積495方呎，屬2房戶，採傳統梗廚設計，以726萬元成交，呎價約14,667元；整個SEASONS系列自去年3月開售至今，累售1,156伙，套現逾71.5億元。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2068272/即時-地產-KOKO-HILLS辦母親節感謝日",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-10 18:26:53",
