        {
            "title": "慈雲山兩7旬鄰居互毆被捕 疑不滿對方入升降機「阻住曬」",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"慈雲山兩名7旬鄰居互毆被捕 疑互相不滿入升降機「阻住曬」\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/063a6c2cb09b651f9683654e7d12cbc8/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250510/_2025051017383216216.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">慈雲山兩名7旬鄰居互毆被捕 疑互相不滿入升降機「阻住曬」</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>慈雲山欣華街10號慈安苑，今日（5月10日）早上11時許，警方接獲一名74歲姓莫女住戶報案，指其71歲弟弟，與70歲姓梁陌生鄰居。在大廈因進出升降機空間而爭執，其間雙方懷疑用手互相襲擊及推撞。\n\n</p>\n<p>人員接報到場，經初步調查，兩人涉嫌在公眾地方打架被捕，現正被扣留調查。案件交由黃大仙區警區刑事調查隊第三隊跟進。衝突中莫翁和梁翁分別口傷及頭痛，清醒被送往伊利沙伯醫院治理。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2068267/即時-港聞-慈雲山兩7旬鄰居互毆被捕-疑不滿對方入升降機-阻住曬",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-10 17:51:22",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "工行買到假黃金？檢測結果：含金量99.99% 疑似雜質為附著物無質量問題",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"工行買到假黃金？檢測結果：含金量99.99%，疑似雜質為附著物。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/4956e88d9eb51fbe3205bdc762d6e3fe/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250510/_2025051017333112600.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">工行買到假黃金？檢測結果：含金量99.99%，疑似雜質為附著物。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>在金價震盪走高引發的「買金」熱潮中，內地一則網友在工行買到疑似「假黃金」的傳聞引發高度關注。最新送檢結果顯示為真金，工行稱客戶對此已認可。\n\n</p><h2>無質量問題</h2>\n<p>近日，有網友在社交平台群聊中稱，朋友在銀行買的金條，熔出時有不明雜質，並發了相關圖片，聊天記錄中提及了工行上海南翔支行，由此引發了眾多網友對該行實物金質量的擔憂與熱議。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3453783/\">天價黃金︱網傳內地銀行賣混雜質金條 網民：中間黑色的是甚麼？</a></strong>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"工行買到假黃金？檢測結果含金量99.99%，沒有品質問題。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/538711a5b24bcc7ece8e5cd08f599af5/2025-05/Clipboard44_0.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        工行買到假黃金？檢測結果含金量99.99%，沒有品質問題。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"工商銀行聲明。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7349c8d21d73137ab11249e487a7066c/2025-05/Clipboard41_1.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        工商銀行聲明。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"「工行買到假黃金」相關話題登熱搜。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8d0d84542416d935e0a7a505d0fed613/2025-05/Clipboard43_0.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        「工行買到假黃金」相關話題登熱搜。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"網民在群組內講述事件經過。大風新聞\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6e2ed192501c3e0c30f61cfb59469a6c/2025-05/216.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        網民在群組內講述事件經過。大風新聞\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"網民指，銀監局已對事件立項。大風新聞\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/26d5333028847f1a0c015a4997830a52/2025-05/626.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        網民指，銀監局已對事件立項。大風新聞\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"網民貼出疑似有問題的金條照片。大風新聞\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b2787c7a13e1c14a36fc7e344663deb3/2025-05/262_5_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        網民貼出疑似有問題的金條照片。大風新聞\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>對此，工行上海市嘉定支行進行了核查並做出情況說明：近期，一位客戶在我支行轄屬南翔支行購買了兩款金條，網傳在上述金條剪開加工過程中發現疑似雜質，經核實，該情況不屬實。\n\n</p>\n<p>工商銀行上海嘉定支行稱，經檢測，兩款金條檢測報告均記載「檢測結論：金含量為99.99%」，無質量問題。經上述質檢機構以專業方式清洗，疑似雜質已脫落，應為金條售出後的外部附著物。以上結論均獲客戶認可。\n\n</p>\n<p>工商銀行上海嘉定支行表示：「工商銀行對所銷售的金條都提供回購服務，請大家放心。同時，也誠懇希望大家不信謠、不傳謠，共同維護良好網絡生態。」<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
